{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In Grand Mall Simulator, you get to manage the shopping mall of your dreams! Your mission is to purchase various boutiques and turn them into thriving stores. Create diverse shopping experiences with outlets for clothing, shoes, hats, groceries, electronics, toys, and much more. Set up shelves, stock them with products, and decorate spaces to attract more customers and increase your mall's popularity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each successful day brings in profits, allowing you to expand and open new boutiques. Additionally, you can automate processes by hiring loaders and merchandisers to ensure shelves are always stocked. The game offers a decoration system that lets you customize the mall to your taste, from furniture arrangements to lighting and style choices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Can you transform a small shopping center into a grand mall?</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327670/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738497878","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327670/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738497878","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327670/0c30f648b448cc4bcddfb38edfa8679ae39e3221/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738497878","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327670/0c30f648b448cc4bcddfb38edfa8679ae39e3221/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738497878","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In Grand Mall Simulator, you get to manage the shopping mall of your dreams! Your mission is to purchase various boutiques and turn them into thriving stores. Create diverse shopping experiences with outlets for clothing, shoes, hats, groceries, electronics, toys, and much more. Set up shelves, sto